main event: Witnesses observed an unidentified object in St. Paul, Minnesota on 8/12/22 at 2330 hours.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 15-20 seconds., The object was described as moving slowly in a small circle., Witnesses reported that the object appeared to be about the size of a small car., The object's color was noted as black and it had a circular shape., No unusual effects were reported on nearby animals or electrical systems.
